1
00:00:01,036 --> 00:00:03,136
<i>When I was a child, I wanted to have</i>

2
00:00:03,136 --> 00:00:06,116
<i>high-heeled shoes, pink nail gloss,</i>

3
00:00:06,116 --> 00:00:08,516
<i>a ring with a pretty stone,</i>

4
00:00:08,516 --> 00:00:12,506
<i>and to become the princess in a fairy tale.</i>

5
00:00:12,506 --> 00:00:14,976
<i>Waiting for the true love kiss from a prince,</i>

6
00:00:14,976 --> 00:00:18,476
<i>I wanted to become the princess in my dreams.</i>

7
00:00:28,196 --> 00:00:30,196
<i>It's 7:30 a.m.!</i>

8
00:00:30,196 --> 00:00:31,886
<i>I like you!</i>

9
00:00:31,886 --> 00:00:33,486
<i>Good morning.</i>

10
00:00:38,030 --> 00:00:46,030
